snippet.title: BLACKHOLE - Launch Trailer (PS4 / Xbox One)
snippet.description:
BLACKHOLE, an award-winning hardcore platformer with over 15 hours of story-driven sci-fi comedy and gravity-twisting puzzles, is AVAILABLE NOW!

One of the top-rated puzzle platformers of 2015 is coming back to Xbox One and PlayStation 4 featuring all available DLC!

https://www.blackhole-game.com/

XBOX ONE: https://www.microsoft.com/store/p/BLACKHOLE-Complete-Edition/BNGDPWK6BJL6

PLAYSTATION 4: https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/blackhole-complete-edition/cid=UP2769-CUSA07080_00-BLACKHOLE001COMP
